github.com/odvcencio/gotreesitter (v0.20.7)
================================================================================

A pure-Go, cgo-free tree-sitter runtime. assayxport uses it (behind the
internal/ts layer) to parse Python source. No source is vendored into this
repository; the module is resolved through the Go module system.

