================================================================================
tree-sitter-python (grammar)
================================================================================

Python support uses the canonical tree-sitter/tree-sitter-python grammar. The
grammar is not vendored here; gotreesitter ships a ts2go-encoded build of it as
an embedded blob (grammars/grammar_blobs/python.bin), decoded at runtime. See
internal/ts/provenance.md for the recorded blob checksum and ABI version.

